summary: A great and free starting home that doesn't require a quest.
descriptionHtml: Creates a location just out of Whiterun called A Secret Cave containing a balanced player home for the beginning or end of the game. It's a small home that's easy to get used too. Also lore friendly. The file will be named TheBungusHouse.esp but everything else will show up in-game as A Secret Cave.
author: AdrienBrody
